songs.title: Swim Up Behind Me
songs.lyrics:
Darling [I had] to see you [up in the mind]
Nothing that I ever said
Only what [are] hiding

Hanging [the right dear] hooks on the line
Soon will be behind me
[swim full of ideas]

Somewhere besides us [for you]
Silently light us [for you]

[Time] comes for you
[Time] [ ] [blue]
